an review (gap a), no specification of competencies for overseers (gap b implied), no technical interface features enabling oversight (gap c), and no deployer obligation enforcement (gap d). At least two specific sub-requirements are clearly identified."}, {"id": "C-014", "verdict": "pass", "confidence": "high", "evidence": "Finding 6: 'Internal model cards exist (TalentLens v3.1, WorkPulse v2.4) and contain detailed architecture, hyperparameter, training data, and performance information, but are marked 'CONFIDENTIAL — Internal Use Only' and prohibited from external distribution. No evidence of external-facing technical documentation package meeting Article 11 requirements (data used for training, design/implementation decisions, performance metrics, known limitations, risks).'", "missing": "", "reasoning": "The memo explicitly identifies that existing documentation does not meet Article 11 technical documentation requirements, noting that internal model cards are confidential/internal-only and no external-facing package exists. The criterion references 'Annex IV' but the memo addresses this under Article 11, which incorporates Annex IV requirements."}, {"id": "C-015", "verdict": "fail", "confidence": "high", "evidence": "Finding 6: 'No evidence of external-facing technical documentation package meeting Article 11 requirements (data used for training, design/implementation decisions, performance metrics, known limitations, risks).'", "missing": "The memo does not identify at least three specific Annex IV items by their Annex IV numbering or with sufficient specificity to match the enumerated Annex IV items (e.g., item numbers 1, 2, 5, 6, 7, 9). The memo references Article 11 requirements generally but does not enumerate specific Annex IV items as missing.", "reasoning": "The PASS condition requires identification of at least three specific Annex IV items. The memo references Article 11 requirements in general terms without mapping to specific numbered Annex IV item