ented procedures for detecting and responding to model drift, discrimination complaints, or performance degradation in production.'", "missing": "The memo identifies the absence of post-deployment monitoring but does not reference Article 72 specifically. The citation in Finding 12 references 'Article 10(3) and (4)' and 'Article 12' but not Article 72.", "reasoning": "The PASS condition requires identification of the missing post-market monitoring system under Article 72 specifically. The memo addresses post-deployment monitoring gaps but attributes them to Articles 10 and 12, not Article 72."}, {"id": "C-031", "verdict": "fail", "confidence": "high", "evidence": "Finding 12 citation: '32024R1689 — Article 10(3) and (4) require ongoing monitoring and post-market surveillance of high-risk AI systems; Article 12 requires deployers to be informed of known issues.'", "missing": "The memo does not note the interconnection between post-market monitoring (Article 72), logging capabilities (Article 12 logging), and the quality management system (Article 17). The memo references Article 12 in connection with informing deployers but not in connection with logging capabilities that enable post-market monitoring.", "reasoning": "The PASS condition requires noting the interdependency between post-market monitoring, logging, and QMS. The memo does not draw these connections, and Article 72 and Article 17 are not referenced."}, {"id": "C-032", "verdict": "fail", "confidence": "high", "evidence": "", "missing": "The memo does not assign any priority level (Critical/High/Medium/Low or equivalent) to any identified gap. The deliverable contains no priority ranking scheme.", "reasoning": "The PASS condition requires a priority level assigned to each or substantially all identified gaps. No such ranking appears anywhere in the deliverable."}, {"id": "C-033", "verdict": "fail", "confidence": "high", "evidence": "", "missing": "No priority ranking exists in the memo, so the incomplete fa