ing 6: 'Internal model cards (TalentLens v3.1, WorkPulse v2.4)...' Finding 14: 'TalentLens Product Guide Section 4.3 uses four confidence score bands...WorkPulse Whitepaper Section 5.1 reports attrition prediction metrics...'", "missing": "", "reasoning": "The memo addresses both TalentLens and WorkPulse with product-specific analysis throughout multiple findings, noting different documentation coverage and product-specific gaps for each system."}, {"id": "C-041", "verdict": "pass", "confidence": "high", "evidence": "Summary: 'Regulation (EU) 2024/1689 Articles 10–13 (high-risk system obligations).' Multiple citations throughout: '32024R1689 — Article 10...' and 'Clauses relied on: EU AI Act Regulation (EU) 2024/1689, Article 10...'", "missing": "", "reasoning": "The memo references the EU AI Act as Regulation (EU) 2024/1689 in the summary and throughout the findings and clauses relied on section."}, {"id": "C-042", "verdict": "fail", "confidence": "high", "evidence": "Articles individually addressed: Article 10 (Findings 1, 4, 9, 12), Article 11 (Findings 1, 6, 10, 13), Article 12 (Findings 2, 3, 4, 7, 11, 12, 14), Article 13 (Findings 5, 11), Article 15 (Finding 8), Article 78(5) (Finding 3).", "missing": "From the required list (Article 9, Article 10, Article 11/Annex IV, Article 12, Article 13, Article 14, Article 15, Article 17, Articles 47-49, Article 72), the memo individually addresses: Article 10, Article 11, Article 12, Article 13, Article 15 — that is 5 articles. Article 9, Article 14, Article 17, Articles 47-49, and Article 72 are not individually addressed. The memo references Article 10 where Article 9 is meant in some places, but Article 9 itself is never cited. The threshold of 7 is not met.", "reasoning": "The PASS condition requires at least 7 of the listed articles to be individually addressed. The deliverable individually addresses only approximately 5 of the listed articles, falling short of the threshold."}, {"id": "C-043", "verdict": "pass", "